Package include: 20 pack kids toothbrush Directions Unroll the toothbrush from its packaging. Wet the toothbrush bristles. Apply a pea-sized amount of toothpaste to the bristles. Hold the toothbrush at a 45-degree angle to the gums. Brush gently in a circular motion. Brush the outer surfaces, inner surfaces, and chewing surfaces of all teeth. Brush the tongue to remove bacteria and freshen breath. Rinse the toothbrush thoroughly after use. Store the toothbrush in a dry, ventilated area.
